# Repository instructions

Start at `docs/README.md` and load only the current semantic owners for the task.
Use repository-local skills under `.agents/skills`. `ARCHITECTURE.md` routes
stable boundaries; product specs own intent, active plans own work state,
runbooks own repeatable operations, and proof packets own claim evidence. Keep
Effects lazy, flat, sequential, and app-executed. Decode at ingress and encode
at outward boundaries. Avoid generic client callbacks, raw semantic identifiers,
primitive semantic config, unchecked output, runtime type-class branching,
pass-through helpers, giant routes, and service-aware presentation leaves. Edit
affected docs in the owning slice and run `bun run verification` before handoff.
